original_title: Dragon Gate The Gate of Maximum 2014 Day 2
overview: Day 2 of Dragon Gate's 2014 Gate of Maximum tour is scheduled to take place on June 5, 2014, at the Korakuen Hall in Tokyo, Japan, and will air on internet Pay-Per-View. The event will feature six matches (including one dark match), before a 5-on-1 scramble elimination match for the rights to the Mad Blankey stable.
title: Dragon Gate The Gate of Maximum 2014 Day 2
